+import React from "react";
+import { Toolbar, Button, Typography, Box } from "@mui/material";
+
+//@ts-ignore
+const RenderTabs = ({ onFilter, onListView, onGraphMode }) => {
+  return (
+    <Toolbar
+      sx={{
+        width: "100%",
+        justifyContent: "space-between",
+        backgroundColor: "white", // 设置背景颜色为白色
+        boxShadow:
+          "0px 2px 4px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.2), 0px 4px 5px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.14), 0px 1px 10px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)", // 添加底部阴影
+      }}
+    >
+      <Typography
+        variant="subtitle1"
+        component="div"
+        sx={{ fontSize: "0.875rem" }}
+      >
+        {" "}
+        // 设置更小的字体大小 RenderTab
+      </Typography>
+      <Box>
+        <Button onClick={onFilter} color="inherit" sx={{ fontSize: "0.75rem" }}>
+          {" "}
+          // 可以选择为按钮设置更小的字体 Filter
+        </Button>
+        <Button
+          onClick={onListView}
+          color="inherit"
+          sx={{ fontSize: "0.75rem" }}
+        >
+          ListView
+        </Button>
+        <Button
+          onClick={onGraphMode}
+          color="inherit"
+          sx={{ fontSize: "0.75rem" }}
+        >
+          GraphMode
+        </Button>
+      </Box>
+    </Toolbar>
+  );
+};
+
+export default RenderTabs;

+import React from "react";
+import { Toolbar, Button, Typography, Box } from "@mui/material";
+
+//@ts-ignore
+const RenderTabs = ({ onFilter, onListView, onGraphMode }) => {
+  return (
+    <Toolbar
+      sx={{
+        width: "100%",
+        justifyContent: "space-between",
+        backgroundColor: "white", // 设置背景颜色为白色

+        {" "}
+        RenderTab
+      </Typography>
+      <Box>
+        <Button onClick={onFilter} color="inherit" sx={{ fontSize: "0.75rem" }}>
+          {" "}
+          // 可以选择为按钮设置更小的字体 Filter
+        </Button>
+        <Button
+          onClick={onListView}
+          color="inherit"
+          sx={{ fontSize: "0.75rem" }}
+        >

+        </Button>
+        <Button
+          onClick={onGraphMode}
+          color="inherit"
+          sx={{ fontSize: "0.75rem" }}
+        >
+          GraphMode
+        </Button>
+      </Box>
+    </Toolbar>
+  );
+};
+
+export default RenderTabs;
